{"tid":1057731,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]《聖鬥士星矢覺醒》（10）人流減半","createTime":"2019-03-12T05:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T06:46:13.000Z","uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85c56f58ad2cd26203bfd8eb4802ab430b0f2185","tid":1057731,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZZy9SRHQQsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZZy9SRHQQsc&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=9b5cbe10\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZZy9SRHQQsc</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajnCOvv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajnCOvv.jpg&h=783ed862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWV1vJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWV1vJ1.jpg&h=e968b68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBH3J4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBH3J4z.jpg&h=3e1e706e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DSGvQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DSGvQ0.jpg&h=d4bb37e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBnGvRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBnGvRi.jpg&h=6753b8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfzxCwk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbfzxCwk.jpg&h=70498eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n26號中午12點開服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://sds.gamamobi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsds.gamamobi.com&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=f8afd73c\" target=\"_blank\">https://sds.gamamobi.com</a><br />\nfacebook:<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sds.Seiya/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsds.Seiya%2F&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=9f409ee5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sds.Seiya/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲介紹</span></span><br />\n隻GAME玩乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻GAME類似陰陽師嘅玩法，收集唔同<del>性</del>聖鬥士<br />\n以6個角色組成一隊，角色出招要用到能量(熟陰陽師嘅可以當佢係火)<br />\n而且可以跨服同其他玩家協力打關，講求合作性同配隊<br />\n玩咩SER好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸GAME手法不嬲興開十九幾個SER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以如果驚追唔上班大課長可以揀比較新嘅SER玩，想抱大腿嘅可以揀SER1(目前比較多巴打玩嘅SER)<br />\n<br />\nSER1軍團 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n加左後麻煩係POST/GAME到PM番團長/副團長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首抽攻略</span></span> <br />\n快刷首抽，一場都唔駛打，之前冇野送就大約1分鐘一次，宜家係唔係有禮物石可以刷多幾下？<br />\n1）開新ac或新set = 50石<br />\n2）抽邪武，右下角分享拎30石（好友分享就得）= 80石<br />\n3）之後佢叫你按劇情，你唔好按劇情個位，是但喺空白位按幾下，佢會問你係咪跳過，揀是<br />\n4）按左上角星矢圖像，擴展下載。拎多20石 = 100石<br />\n*宜家新ac好似有獎勵，總共會有300幾石可以抽3下<br />\n抽野，中就開唔中就切換帳號由頭嚟過<br />\n=========<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">首抽建議</span></span><br />\n1.雙子座撒卡<br />\n目前全GAME最高群體傷兼無視敵方念防(魔防)，培養難度低，新手抽中佢一開始可以無腦過關<br />\n2.雙魚座阿布羅狄<br />\n輸出系，只要留能量比佢到最後可以一波打死人，傷害唔講得少<br />\n3.天蠍座米羅<br />\n同樣係輸出系，優勝之處係唔需要用到能量去出技而且主要輸出係1技，運用方法係出2技＞1技去做輸出，配合B級角六分儀可以即時做出一套連技，不過好食技書去升技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />課長可以無視以上嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.白羊座穆<br />\n全GAME最勁嘅神坦，可以幫自己/隊友開盾而且仲會吸收盾所受到嘅傷害再用3技出真傷還番比人，反擊流必要隊員之一<br />\n5.水瓶座卡妙<br />\n冰隊核心隊員，配合冰河可以成為現時最流行嘅冰隊，2技可以冰人一回合，3技因應對面疊加嘅印記而提高傷害<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛開始國服抽卡不給碎片，但現在改限時抽卡活動會有碎片給，變相保底但還是得抽夠一定次數的量，神沙屬於特典活動，國服活動結束不入一般卡池，有能力務必抽到，有些卡是必要的，就像有神沙跟沒神沙是兩個遊戲，刚开服其实不用特别去抽那个S卡，存星石等候面卡出来在抽，脸好会附带不少S出现。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">by結蕉渠蓋龜苓膏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">小字宙</span></span></span><br />\n小宇宙類似以前魔靈同陰陽師嘅符文同魂咁 都係用黎幫角色提升能力值<br />\n而且會有唔同效果<br />\n以下係轉自巴哈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/205621_1bf998eb165c2403c14e51664ea4bcfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F205621_1bf998eb165c2403c14e51664ea4bcfa.png&h=1a5a38ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/205620_4ac45d411b91c0eea56b606bfcadaa4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F205620_4ac45d411b91c0eea56b606bfcadaa4d.png&h=56658a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抽野傳說及其他攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ruan8.com/gonglue/9742.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ruan8.com%2Fgonglue%2F9742.html&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5967d4fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ruan8.com/gonglue/9742.html</a><br />\n超級實用攻略 轉自巴哈<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33366&amp;snA=78&amp;tnum=95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D33366%26snA%3D78%26tnum%3D95&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=220f66ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33366&amp;snA=78&amp;tnum=95</a><br />\n<br />\n1001開POST template<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=38814bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"ac57d9ae68b23b94fc40c613316b2829b56a37f5","tid":1057731,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"終於到我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406b01f0ad21f5995da616602a2b5a3d3f5c1c39","tid":1057731,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"有兩個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bb000344597018019baea696e0e94ab600d300","tid":1057731,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406b01f0ad21f5995da616602a2b5a3d3f5c1c39","tid":1057731,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"有兩個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"入佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以爲我係1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f7a848ed699d6c6b44c477fdc08711c702a68d","tid":1057731,"uid":38321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bb000344597018019baea696e0e94ab600d300","tid":1057731,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406b01f0ad21f5995da616602a2b5a3d3f5c1c39","tid":1057731,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"有兩個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:46:33.000Z","m